## Success criteria (testable)

Project is "done" when ALL of these are true:

[VARIABLE: SUCCESS_CRITERIA — 3-5 bullets, each verifiable]

Each criterion must be one of:
- **Artifact on disk**: `file at path/to/file.ext exists and contains [X]`
- **Command returns 0**: `bash verify/final.sh exits 0`
- **Demonstrable behavior**: `opening X in browser shows Y`

Not allowed: "users are happy", "code is clean", "works well."

